will provide gasoline engines for forklifts to Toyota's forklift
manufacturing subsidiary in Indiana, while Aisin Seiki Co. of the
Toyota group will supply power shift transmissions to the Nissan
subsidiary.
     The Toyota and Nissan subsidiaries in the U.S. are to begin
production of forklifts in July and the summer, respectively.



