said.
     The accused, including two-star Gen. Zaheer Ulislam Abbasi and
Brig. Mustansar Billa, have refused to accept the charge sheet but
are being defended by a retired justice, family members of one of the
defendants said.
     The five-man military court headed by Maj. Gen. Zahid Ehsan has
